<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Dscant" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Déscant,</orth> vb. 1) to sing: <cit><quote>while thou on Tereus --est better skill,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 1134" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1134</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) to comment: <cit><quote>to d. on the doubts of my decay,</quote> <bibl n="shak. pp 184" default="NO" valid="yes">Pilgr. 184</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>and d. on mine own deformity,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 1.1.27" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 1, 27</bibl></cit>.
